1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,316
The pathologic cascade proceeds in four

2
00:00:03,316 --> 00:00:03,868
steps.

3
00:00:03,868 --> 00:00:07,184
Direct viral injury or immune-mediated attack

4
00:00:07,184 --> 00:00:10,500
triggers T-cell infiltration and a cytokine

5
00:00:10,500 --> 00:00:11,053
