6
00:00:11,053 --> 00:00:13,263
Myocyte necrosis releases troponin.

7
00:00:13,263 --> 00:00:16,579
Edema, fibrosis, and impaired contractility produce

8
00:00:16,579 --> 00:00:19,895
the ventricular dysfunction that underlies every

9
00:00:19,895 --> 00:00:21,000
downstream complication.
